          Step into the heart of Cast Design Fireplaces, where family, passion, and craftsmanship intertwine to create timeless beauty. Founded over 20 years ago by Joel, a visionary artisan with a love for design and a knack for crafting cast stone masterpieces, our journey began with a simple yet profound mission: to bring affordable luxury to every home.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a family-owned business, we believe in the power of connection — both with our customers and within our own ranks. From Joel's expert craftsmanship to the tireless dedication of his daughter, brother, and the entire Cast Design Fireplaces family, our shared commitment to excellence shines through in every project we undertake.
        </p>
        <p>
          With over two decades of experience designing, creating, and installing cast stone products across the DFW metroplex, Joel's passion for perfection has never wavered. From humble beginnings to a legacy of elegance, Cast Design Fireplaces continues to redefine the art of luxury fireplace design, one mantel at a time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Join us as we write the next chapter in our story, where every flame illuminates the warmth of family, the beauty of craftsmanship, and the promise of a hearth that feels like home. Welcome to the Cast Design Fireplaces family — where your dreams are our inspiration.
        </p>
